appDetails.recentChangesHtml:

- enemy fighters will now make an effort to avoid crashing into you

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- New plane. Pretty ahistorical. Requires ALL medals, so chances are you won't be flying it anyway.
- New optional control scheme. Default for new players. Basically it does away with switching weapons and instead you have separate triggers for every weapon.
- Misc stuff like some extra flavor, new explosion effects, bullet time when you're about to ram an enemy fighter, nicer main menu.
- Google's mandatory SDK updates.
